title: New: Celeste – Born Again
content: Having featured on a TIEKS single earlier in the year, 19 year old Londoner (originally from Culver City, CA) Celeste, steps out with her debut solo track, Born Again. Self-written and produced by Tev’n, it’s an exploration of her soulful, pensive vocals, set against a nostalgic electronic backdrop. For a first release, it’s mighty confident, and will undoubtedly see her making inroads in all the right places. Check out Born Again below.
